ej,alomr001,P,hirsj901,Called third strike $Roberto Alomar argued the called third strike and HP umpire John Hirschbeck yelled back at Alomar; the argument escalated and Alomar spat on Hirschbeck; Alomar was suspended five games at the start of the 1997 season
$umpire crew chief Jim McKean kept John Hirschbeck out of the game due to the emotional confrontation between Hirschbeck and Roberto Alomar the previous day
